projects.title: NeuroNerd
projects.description: Created by using Django, Python3, Postgresql and Vue, NeuroNerd is an application for people who are interested in neuroscience. It was fun combining two of my biggest interests: neuroscience and computer science!

projects.title: On My Block
projects.description: Inspired to keep neighborhoods and residents safe, On My Block is an app for locals to see and post crimes and recommendations as well as 'like' recommendations in their neighborhood. Featuring User Authentication, this app was created with MongoDB, Postgresql, React Router, Express and Node.js.

projects.title: Travel Bucket List
projects.description: A full stack MERN travel app for people interested in traveling to Australia. With full CRUD, people can add, delete and update experiences they want to have as well as travel tips.
